Spatz,<br>
   You asked if anyone here was willing to stand up to Hitler.  I AM!  I was thinking about what it is about you that draws so much disdain and so little pity.  I was the kid on the playground who stood up for kids like you when the rest of the class was pummelling him.  I really did some soul searching to understand why I find it so hard to feel any compassion for you... Why I feel that there is actually something healthy going on here amongst all this sickness...I came to this conclusion:<br><br>
Because you are delusional, egocentric, maniacal, misogynistic, deceitful, hysterical, megalomaniacal and seem to carry a kind of reverse charisma you are ultimately dangerous.  As those terms came to mind the comparrison to Hitler also came to mind.  He too was a lifelong outcast who not only wanted to be accepted, but needed his way.  He had once been laughed at, but had proven how lethal that kind of personality can be.<br><br>
Yes, I will stand up to you/him!<br><br>
Your threat to Ed's daughter was more than a mere outburst.  Child protective services need to look into you.<br><br>
I know where you live...4th St. E., parked between two freeways, a block in either direction.  Barry, I know that you are home tonight.  By the way, Santa Ana is more than a brisk walk to any of the Ritz Carltons and the only beach your jogging on is the sewer line.  It's not that we care...I believe that most of us have 'been there, done that...people of character care about things of much greater value than anything you could buy or cajole...something you will obviously never understand...not if you haven't gotten it by now.<br><br>
I am very sincere when I suggest that you get professional help.  If you truly do have a daughter, do it for her.<br><br>
ANNE<br><br>

